@@TJvExDBGrid
Summary
  Base class for extended data-aware grids.
Description
  TJvExDBGrid is a base class for classes in the JVCL library that descend from TDBGrid.
  
  Do not create instances of TJvExDBGrid. The TJvDBGrid class provides a generic implementation of
  TJvExDBGrid. You can also create your own descendant class.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvExCustomDBGrid.OnParentColorChange
Summary
  Occurs when the color property for the parent of the control changes.
Description
  \Write an OnParentColorChange event to take specific action when the ParentColor property changes.

